payOuts(uint256).details: allows users to claim their weekly interests       updates the totalRewards earned by the user on a particular investment       Total interest is divided into the number of weeks during the lockUpPeriod       The remaining weekly interests(if any) will be withdrawn at the time of claiming the particular interestAccount.
